{"Id":489,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-muhammadmakin","Author":"Muhammad Makin","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://quranenc.com/check/chinese_makin/v1.0.0-csv.1 , https://quranenc.com/en/browse/chinese_makin , https://quranenc.com ,","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":41,"Text":"敬畏的人们，必定在树荫之下，清泉之滨，"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":42,"Text":"享受他们爱吃的水果，"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":43,"Text":"将对他们说：“你们曾经行善，故你们痛快地饮食吧！”"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":44,"Text":"我必定要这样报酬行善者。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":45,"Text":"在那日，伤哉否认真理的人们。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":46,"Text":"你们暂时吃喝享受吧！你们确是犯罪的人。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":47,"Text":"在那日，伤哉否认真理的人们。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":48,"Text":"有人对他们说：你们当鞠躬。他们不肯鞠躬。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":49,"Text":"在那日，伤哉否认真理的人们。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":50,"Text":"除《古兰经》外，他们要信仰什么文辞呢？"}]}